    "description": "<p>Powerful magick-users and spellcasters that have the strength and power of artillery. They very often channel the teachings of either destruction gods (such as Siwa Priests or Nibatala Katalonan) or rely on the knowledge of old mystic arts passed down from generations.</p>",
